{"tid":356996,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"又睇完一套漫畫 惡之華","createTime":"2017-08-12T14:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T11:57:23.000Z","uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"80e82f3da9eda77e58d2f6b2f490cee2b9e385fd","tid":356996,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:13:38.000Z","msg":"有幾多都睇唔明<br />\n<br />\n不過一開始睇男主睇咁撚多書 仲要睇咁難既哲學書就知佢睇唔撚明<br />\n因為小弟都試過睇尼采 <br />\n<br />\n用書來打飛機想區別自己同其他人<br />\n自己一開波咪又係同其他人即係肥仔同毒撚同學一樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明點解想燒自己個Part 唔同女神扑野個part 幾多都睇唔明<br />\n<br />\n第二部去左第二個城市<br />\n主角溝女係因為佢開始唔再咁憎其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n男主發夢係想講對未來生活既期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結局 睇唔太明 係4眼女覺得自己搵到同類 唔洗再孤獨落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249835b7577ccd9e97eb40b4001739a4bf52c41f","tid":356996,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:17:15.000Z","msg":"屌你又偷偷負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b871ca5e16229c2afae15a54e164aa0fd8df90","tid":356996,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24e0a30b0ccad9a511daec3626df47d013b30e91","tid":356996,"uid":126857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T15:27:42.000Z","msg":"其實前面幾好 第一次睇個陣好吸引 再加埋動畫首ed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c98f9217020094dd2f79742ce822bbcad1643581","tid":356996,"uid":78149,"lik